  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of MT-1303 in Subjects With Moderate to Severe Active Crohn's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Multicentre, Randomised, Double-Blind, Parallel Group, Placebo Controlled Study to Evaluate Safety, Tolerability and Clinical Efficacy of MT-1303 in Subjects With Moderate to Severe Active Crohn's Disease</official_title>
